Package: pxR2
Type: Package
Title: Read and Write PX Data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Emil", "Westin", , "emilwestin@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: The goal of pxR2 is to provide a faster and easier way to read 
  and write px-data (PC-AXIS), inspired by the packages pxR and readr.
  It is designed to correctly parse data and metadata and easy integration
  with other px-related programs such as PXjob and PXEdit.
